39:11.000 --> 39:20.000
I would like to say a few words about marketing services and the differentiation and positioning of marketing services.

39:20.000 --> 39:25.000
Many Russian companies are not food manufacturers.

39:25.000 --> 39:28.000
Small and medium-sized businesses are business services.

39:28.000 --> 39:35.000
It concerns restaurants, shops and wholesale and retail activities.

39:35.000 --> 39:38.000
And we face an unusual element here.

39:38.000 --> 39:47.000
We face the need to position ourselves, on the other hand, with the difficulties of what is called «your own service».

39:47.000 --> 39:57.000
The difference between a service and a product is that a service simultaneously implies both the material and non-material part of a person.

39:57.000 --> 40:05.000
If any of you have studied marketing in detail before, for example, at the university or at separate seminars,

40:05.000 --> 40:10.000
you probably know that a service is characterized by the property of «non-permanence of quality».

40:10.000 --> 40:12.000
What does it mean?

40:12.000 --> 40:26.000
If people are involved in the business process, they are not ready to perform the same procedure with the «permanence of quality» as automated robots.

40:26.000 --> 40:33.000
For example, we come to the same restaurant and get a different quality dish.

40:33.000 --> 40:39.000
We come to the same hairdresser and get a different haircut.

40:39.000 --> 40:45.000
This «non-permanence of quality» leads to the fact that when we talk about the differentiation and positioning of services,

40:45.000 --> 40:50.000
we face the need for the inseparability of the company's activities and marketing.

40:50.000 --> 40:52.000
This is a very important element.

40:52.000 --> 41:04.000
Marketing as a function of one or two people in the company, in industrial companies, is replaced by marketing of all services.

41:04.000 --> 41:15.000
If you open a restaurant, hotel, hairdresser or store, you know that your marketing and advertising are worthless

41:15.000 --> 41:22.000
if your employees who contact the client do not demonstrate a marketing approach to them.

41:22.000 --> 41:33.000
The second feature of marketing services that we constantly encounter is that the service is not protected by patents.

41:33.000 --> 41:48.000
Therefore, we observe a phenomenon in the service when competitors copy our slogans, innovations, approaches and positioning.

41:48.000 --> 42:00.000
This is why marketing services require alternating approaches, a constant desire to keep the consumer in tension, a constant creativity.

42:00.000 --> 42:06.000
You cannot, having once invented a slogan, be sure that customers will come to you for years.

42:06.000 --> 42:14.000
You will have to push them to come to you all the time with a new approach based on one of the eight models of differentiation.

42:14.000 --> 42:23.000
The third problem of differentiation and positioning of services is that in marketing services,

42:23.000 --> 42:27.000
control over the interaction of the client's employee is very difficult.

42:27.000 --> 42:33.000
This is what creates the basis for earning money for small business.

42:33.000 --> 42:38.000
It is not an anonymous product, but a relationship with the employee and the client.

42:38.000 --> 42:54.000
Since it is difficult to reproduce the quality of the employee's service, we face the fact that any bad mood can affect the client's service.

42:54.000 --> 43:04.000
Therefore, there is a whole wheel of service that shows that if you want to have a good service, you must have motivated employees.

43:04.000 --> 43:15.000
Therefore, the problem of controlling the interaction of the employee and the client is faced with how comfortable the employee feels today.

43:15.000 --> 43:22.000
Is he not ready to pour his indignation at the boss or internal conflicts in the company on his consumers?

43:22.000 --> 43:33.000
This is a very difficult problem because not a single supervisor and not a single company manager can be present all the time in the negotiation with the employee and the client.

43:33.000 --> 43:37.000
The problem with the growth of the company is even more important for marketing services.

43:37.000 --> 43:44.000
I said that in marketing services the most important thing is the person providing the service.

43:44.000 --> 43:54.000
When a company grows, the previous differentiation, the previous ideology, culture of the company that creates the basis of differentiation begins to blur.

43:54.000 --> 44:04.000
Therefore, fast-growing companies lose the most in differentiation and need it most in the new repositioning.

44:04.000 --> 44:13.000
The problem of labor productivity is due to the fact that we cannot make a person do many times more than he does today.

44:13.000 --> 44:22.000
Yes, we can buy more efficient machines, but we cannot make the waiter serve not 10, but 100 people.

44:22.000 --> 44:41.000
The problem of innovation. It is not a secret that in marketing services, innovations are welcomed, but they can be offered much less than innovations in technology or production.

44:41.000 --> 44:51.000
And finally, in any country there are restrictive standards related to work and personnel, and, accordingly, this suggests that this limits our differentiation.

44:51.000 --> 44:58.000
We cannot provide a 24-hour service if employees have to go to work in 8 hours.

44:58.000 --> 45:04.000
In addition, you understand that different employees provide different services.

45:04.000 --> 45:07.000
The machine can work 24 hours, the employee cannot.

45:07.000 --> 45:14.000
In this regard, I would like to tell a funny story. Bad news for business services.

45:14.000 --> 45:22.000
If you are in business, the problem of positioning is very important for you.

45:22.000 --> 45:28.000
You will have to compete with Nordstrom, Disneyland and McDonald's. What does this mean?

45:28.000 --> 45:46.000
When we are engaged in service, we often have to do not only better than our direct competitors, but often do better than those service companies that our client encounters.

45:46.000 --> 45:52.000
